### ============================================================
### 8. ACTUATOR (public, no auth required)
### ============================================================

### Health check
GET http://localhost:8080/actuator/health

###

### Prometheus metrics
GET http://localhost:8080/actuator/prometheus


### ============================================================
### 9. ROLE-BASED ACCESS TESTS
### ============================================================

### Deployer can deploy
POST {{baseUrl}}/definitions/validate
Authorization: Bearer {{deployer_token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="example-order-process.bpmn"
Content-Type: application/xml

< {{bpmnFile}}
--boundary--

###

### Viewer can read definitions
GET {{baseUrl}}/definitions
Authorization: Bearer {{viewer_token}}

###

### Viewer CANNOT start instances (expect 403)
POST {{baseUrl}}/instances
Authorization: Bearer {{viewer_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "definitionKey": "order-processing",
  "variables": {"orderAmount": 100}
}

###

### Operator can start instances
POST {{baseUrl}}/instances
Authorization: Bearer {{operator_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "definitionKey": "order-processing",
  "variables": {"orderAmount": 100, "customerId": "cust-test"}
}

###

### Viewer can read history
GET {{baseUrl}}/history/instances/{{instance_id}}/events
Authorization: Bearer {{viewer_token}}

###

### No token — expect 401
GET {{baseUrl}}/definitions
